ams to fit the position requirements in addition we offer an excellent portfolio of spiral dryer fabrics for those applications with special requirements  roll covers xeriums stowe woodward roll cover product portfolio includes premium performance rubber polyurethane and composite technology engineered specifically for each application our innovative products are the standard by which roll technology is measured   spreader rolls xeriums stowe and mount hope bowed spreader rolls products provide highperformance web and fabric smoothing for the most demanding applications in addition our portfolio includes all metal rolls as well as specially engineered sleeves for high temperature and high speed applications smart® technology xeriums roll product portfolio includes stowe roll covers stowe and mount hope bowed spreader rolls and smart® technology our roll cover products are engineered for each papermaking machine  our patented smart® technology uses embedded sensors in roll covers to dynamically measure nip conditions across numerous sections of the machine mechanical services xerium offers a full range of rollrelated repairs and upgrades from ontherun otr roll analysis vibration analysis internal inspection  repair optical  laser alignment suction box overhauls to new shell constructions and much more     xerium technologies inc all rights reserved site developed by corpcomm group inc about us  terms  conditions  privacy policy for our north american customers  for our north amerian suppliers  employment ca supply chains act xerium technologies inc docket item   united states courts archive youre viewing docket item  from the case xerium technologies inc view the full docket and case details download this document view plain text appendix c to superpriority priming senior secured debtorinpossession credit and guaranty agreement term loan commitments bank citicorp north america inc tennenbaum dip opportunity fund llc total term loan commitment       pro rata share    